@JoseleBernabe Hi Josele,
We are sorry to hear that your luggage wasn't duly delivered. Please send us your concern or reimbursement request via the following link https://t.co/DlPk2wk146. Our respective colleagues will take of your submission. Thank you for your patience.
Best regards, Shawn

@xslime296 Hi there, 
Thank you for getting in touch. Please send us your booking code via PM, so we can take a closer look.
Best regards, Shawn

@cd10v07 Hi Charlotte, 
I'm sorry to hear your luggage wasn't duly delivered. Have you done a delayed or lost report yet? Please feel free to use the following link; https://t.co/DlPk2wk146 in order to fill out the online form. 
Best regards, Shawn

@helenarvan Hello Helen,
Thank you for your message! We are very glad that you enjoyed your trip and appreciate your feedback! We look forward to welcoming you on board again! 
Best regards, Gayle

Vielen Dank für die Blumen, lieber @TilSchweiger ! Deine Lieblingsairline bietet übrigens auch Flugangstseminare an https://t.co/Ir2j7NCNyD! 😎🛫
@ORFWillkommenOe @grissemann @stermann @ORF 

https://t.co/taFiMHrzOU

@woahwoahbrodie Hello, 
Thanks for your message! Your baggage allowance is based on the fare you purchased. Kindly send us your booking code via DM, so we can have a closer look at your request. 
Best regards, Gayle

@badoer77 Lieber Lukas, 
vielen Dank für deine Nachricht! Wie können wir dir behilflich sein?
Liebe Grüße, Gayle

@eugenej89312567 Hello Eugene, 
I'm sorry to hear your luggage wasn't duly delivered. Please be assured that our colleagues are working around the clock to process each bag and reunite passengers with their luggage. We kindly ask for your patience.
Best regards, Gayle

@EugeneJ89312567 (2/2)  
We thank you in advance for your understanding and patience.
Best regards, Alessandra

@EugeneJ89312567 (1/2) Hi Eugene,
your inquiry has been forwarded to our Feedback Management department and is currently pending!
Please note, due to high number of emails at the moment, the processing time takes longer. My colleagues do their utmost to answer your request as soon as possible.

@Duck_Malakes Hi,
I really do understand your frustration, and while I cannot give you a precise timeline as to when your claim will be processed, I can assure you that the team is working hard to get back to you as soon as possible. We really do appreciate your patience. 
Best regards, Mae

@pprcomms @frankbarrettmos Hello, 
We are sorry to hear about your father's experience and can only apologize for any inconvenience caused. If you haven't sent your feedback yet to Customer Relations, please do so via https://t.co/FFefe6Jqyt 
Best regards, Gayle

@gatoxxerran @paulussporidis @unlimapps Hi, 
I'm very sorry you haven't received a response yet. Please be assured that our colleagues are doing their utmost to answer all requests. Kindly DM us the file reference of your case, so we can have a look. 
Best regards, Gayle

@justcallmecase Hi there, 
Our flights are the most charming way to fly. 😉 Please let us know, how we can assist you. 
Best regards, Shawn

@lukeoregan88 Hi Luke, we are very pleased to receive your praise. Your words are a source of motivation for us and our colleagues on board in particular, who are always striving to offer great service. 
We look forward to welcoming you onboard again soon!
Best regards, Denis
